@startuml
!include ../_style.puml

title Container Diagram

skinparam nodesep 30
skinparam ranksep 55
skinparam ArrowFontSize 11
skinparam roundCorner 12

skinparam component<<service>> {
  BackgroundColor #E8F1FC
  BorderColor #2C5C8F
}
skinparam component<<infra>> {
  BackgroundColor #F0F0F0
  BorderColor #666666
}
skinparam database {
  BackgroundColor #FFF3D6
  BorderColor #B58900
}

actor "User\n[Person]" as User
actor "Admin\n[Person]" as Admin

rectangle "RAM-USB System" {

  component "**Entry-Hub**\n[Go]\nPublic API gateway" as EntryHub <<service>>
  component "**Security-Switch**\n[Go]\nRequest re-validation" as SecuritySwitch <<service>>
  component "**Database-Vault**\n[Go]\nRe-validation, identity\nstorage & crypto" as DatabaseVault <<service>>
  component "**Storage-Service**\n[Go, SFTP]\nEncrypted backup storage" as StorageService <<service>>
  component "**Network-Manager**\n[Go]\nMesh & ACL orchestration" as NetworkManager <<service>>

  database "**PostgreSQL**\nUser identity records" as Postgres

  component "**Certificate-Authority**\n[smallstep/certificates]\nmTLS issuance & rotation" as CA <<infra>>
  component "**Observability**\n[Mosquitto, Metrics-Collector,\nGrafana, TimescaleDB]\nMetrics pipeline & dashboards" as Observability <<infra>>
}

User -down-> EntryHub : **HTTPS**\nregister / login / health
EntryHub -down-> SecuritySwitch : **mTLS**
SecuritySwitch -down-> DatabaseVault : **mTLS**
DatabaseVault -right-> Postgres : **SQL**
DatabaseVault <-down-> StorageService : **mTLS**\ncreate POSIX user / fetch public key
SecuritySwitch -right-> NetworkManager : **mTLS**\nACL grant / pre-auth key
EntryHub -right-> NetworkManager : **Headscale coordination**\n(reverse-proxied)

User --> StorageService : **SFTP**\nbackup / restore

Admin -down-> Observability : **HTTPS**\ndashboards

@enduml
